<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="thus-adv">thus <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðʌs/    美 /ðʌs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>如此；这样</strong></h4>
<p>in this way; like this：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Neither pour out all you know nor remark all you see thus to keep a quiet life. 
知道的不要全部倾吐，看到的不要都评论，这样生活才可以平静。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>因而；从而</strong></h4>
<p>(therefore)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We failed to find enough evidence; thus we concluded that he was innocent. 
我们未能找到足够的证据，因此，我们认定他是无罪的。</p></div></div>